JLtools 0.9
		    JLtools Extensible Compiler Toolkit

Build Instructions
------------------

First ensure javac is in your path and that you are using JDK 1.2
or later.  

On Unix, do:

	sh ./configure
	make

On NT, you will need the Cygwin environment. While running sh, do:

	sh ./configure
	make
    
For more information:
---------------------

For information on specific Java language extensions included with
this release (e.g. Jif, PolyJ, etc.), see the appropriate README-*
file in this directory.


